      "description": "Align trimmed reads to a reference genome. Method neutrality: the concrete\naligner (STAR / HISAT2 / BWA-MEM2 / minimap2 / Bowtie2 / Salmon-alevin)\nis selected at runtime by the agent. EDAM operation:3198 (Read mapping)\nis the more-specific child of operation:0292 (Sequence alignment).\n",
